      "span_text": "fracture within the cervical third of the tooth, placement of sub-gingival restorative margins, and restorations which violate the biologic width.  Cases with deep fracture requiring excessive bone removal, non-restorable teeth, teeth with inadequate crown-root ratio, increased risk"
